title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Wonbo...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Yes...?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Could you go all the way to the end of this river,
And then come all the way back and tell me if it's even worth going?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
I'm serious. I don't want to tire myself out.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Fine.
<<BeginKayakGameplay DialogueSwitcher>>
